  "title": "Nagaland University",
  "meta_description": "Established under the Nagaland University Act, 1989, Nagaland University is the 13th Central University of India and the only Central University in Nagaland. Officially operational since September 6, 1994, it has its headquarters at Lumami with campuses in Kohima and Medziphema. The University offers a wide range of UG, PG, and Ph.D. programs across 44 departments and has 69 affiliated colleges across the state.",
